parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the EPS system can cause the power steering assist to fail, making the steering wheel difficult to turn, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The EPS warning light illuminates
the power steering assist fails
the steering wheel is difficult to turn
the steering wheel makes abnormal clicking or grinding sounds
the steering wheel seizes or becomes stuck.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause the power steering assist to fail, making the steering wheel difficult to turn, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The steering column makes abnormal clicking or grinding sounds
the steering wheel seizes or becomes stuck
the steering wheel is difficult to turn.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clockspring can cause the power steering assist to fail, making the steering wheel difficult to turn, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The clockspring fails
the power steering assist fails
the steering wheel is difficult to turn.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering coupler can cause the power steering assist to fail, making the steering wheel difficult to turn, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The steering coupler fails
the power steering assist fails
the steering wheel is difficult to turn.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the vehicle occupants are not protected from the impact.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
even at high speeds or with significant impact.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unwanted airbag deployment can cause injuries, especially if the deployment occurs while the vehicle is in motion, and can also lead to accidents.
symptoms: Airbags deploy unexpectedly
without a crash or impact
while the vehicle is in motion or parked.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag warning light can indicate a problem with the airbag system, which can lead to a failure to deploy in a crash or unwanted deployment.
symptoms: The airbag warning light on the dashboard stays on
indicating a problem with the airbag system.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Clock Spring or SRS Module Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the clock spring or SRS module can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to a failure to deploy in a crash or unwanted deployment.
symptoms: The airbag warning light on the dashboard stays on
indicating a problem with the airbag system
and the clock spring or SRS module is faulty.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
warning lights on the dashboard
battery drain
and difficulties with starting the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose braking ability, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the vehicle takes longer to stop
and the brake warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the alarm system can cause the vehicle to become a nuisance, and in some cases, lead to battery drain or other electrical issues.
symptoms: The alarm goes off randomly
the alarm does not turn off
and the vehicle's electrical system is affected.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the windows and doors can cause inconvenience and discomfort to the driver and passengers.
symptoms: The windows do not roll up or down
the doors do not lock or unlock
and the window motors fail.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can cause the airbags to deploy unnecessarily or not deploy in the event of a crash, leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag deploys unnecessarily
and the passenger airbag does not function properly.
